			<td colspan="2" bgcolor="#DEDACB" background="http://www.everlore.com/gimages/tb_beige.gif">
		
				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				Finding this spell may be a little tricky, because they are not sold where you buy the rest of your spells (to my knowledge, this is true in every city).<BR>
Normally, you buy your spells at a merchant that sells spells for your class only. However, there are some spells, such as Gate, the different shielding spells, true north, root (which can be used by any other caster than mage), etc.<BR>
All these spells are sold by a merchant that is not connected to any specific caster guild. In Ak'anon, you find this merchant in the room you enter, when you go inside the library. In Freeport, you find this merchant along with the merchant that sells different kinds of stones (two ladies by the entrance to the library).
				</font>
			</td>

	</tr>
	
